    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My universe, my world, my nation, my city,  &lt;br&gt;
my religion, my society, my family, my child,  &lt;br&gt;
my mother, my sister, my body, my hand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Did you observe the gradation of my-ness increasing?  &lt;br&gt;
This is how relationship grading happens in our life.  &lt;br&gt;
We try to defend, protect, and fight for the closest first  &lt;br&gt;
and then the next one.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
